Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼樣 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這就降下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}已經撐不住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}飛的時間一長 下面果然會很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔女都這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}都會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是其他魔女似乎沒這個煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我騎乘的姿勢不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不是啦 借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}訣竅呢 就是別想著騎掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你看了就知道 睜大眼睛看好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一聽到飛翔 很多人都會想到騎掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但其實是像這樣 讓身體一起浮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔 只讓掃帚飄起來 所以騎著才會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}其實身體只是陪襯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}掃帚才是消除重力的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想通這一點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害的對話
