Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 再來練一次 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}以前的魔女不一定要靠掃帚飛行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比方說豬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 跨在豬身上飛 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}帥氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭 你這是在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}除草啊 除草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在和真琴一起種蔬菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幫田地除草 順便把住家周圍的草也拔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大好的高中年華 放假卻要幫忙農事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭可真是個怪孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐才是 高中輟學跑去了香港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只是忍不住想見成龍一眼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(1132.5,982.5)}Jackie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Jackie？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}身體只是陪襯 只是陪襯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}茜姐 你能在這裡待多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的旅行告一段落了 想先休息一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大姐姐 今天也住我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 我想再住上幾天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的 再一起洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大姐姐要留下來住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭 我能抱走她嗎 太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這得問問爸媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請收我為徒 讓我成為魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏 你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這一陣子看著真琴姐和大姐姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}感覺魔女真是可愛又帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也想當魔女 放放魔法 騎掃帚飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以收我為徒 教我如何施放魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}普通女孩也能當魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能倒是能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}耶 能當魔女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}等一下等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這可是相當重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以不是我們說了算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總之先問問爸爸媽媽的意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後再做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這個要求很麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一般人要成為魔女可得吃不少苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一不小心 可能連一般人的生活都過不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想奈奈阿姨也知道這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想問個很重要的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽說「哇 魔女？去吧去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}爸爸也在電話裡說「真帥啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還是這麼善解人意的父母呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那可以收我為徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我沒有在收徒弟 所以沒辦法輕易答應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大姐姐 拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}都這樣求你了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎樣求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 這麼辦吧 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}接下來我要讓你看不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不少東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對 不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不是你這陣子所認識到的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}而是更深入一層的魔女世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比方說魔女的工作 娛樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}傳統儀式啊 我們之外的魔女等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想見識一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我給你一個體驗學習的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}先全部看過嘗試過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再決定當不當魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 我答應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 在此之前任命你為見習魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不錯啊 當上魔女了喔 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}見習魔女也是貨真價實的魔女喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多指教 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 感覺抓到竅門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我終於能稍微飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}押忍 今後請多指教 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:25.27,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※押忍\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}武術專用問候語，相當於你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}彼此彼此…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嚇我一跳 千夏要當魔女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還只是見習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔女的數量正不斷減少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這對魔女界來說可是好消息呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是要注意點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當上魔女這件事要跟身邊人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}雖然我來說沒有說服力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當上魔女該做什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這倒沒有強制規定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}基本上做什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼都可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比如製作藥劑來販售
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}學些魔法來玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}或者像犬養小姐那樣 成為一名占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也可以像姐姐那樣 環遊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是每位魔女的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但不能拿來做壞事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐要做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老實說 其實我還不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但我的理想是成為能幫上身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也能讓自己得到幸福的魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}跟英雄一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哪裡哪裡 過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}學會了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想變出輛南瓜馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再讓玩具動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還想變出糖果屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不錯呢 很棒的夢想喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它會大口大口地吃掉進來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}騙你的 我會好好想想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭是電影迷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}談不上影迷 但的確喜歡看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我以前上過電影喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎 好厲害 什麼電影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}超冷門的片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很難為情的 片名就保密啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是謎團重重的姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下一部就看這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}買回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 你吩咐的都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很好 那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大姐姐簡單易懂的魔法講座 第二講
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請掌聲歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這次是教什麼魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這次我們來製作一些「奇怪的點心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:23.32,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※日文的奇怪和點心皆有「おかし」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請別在意我說的冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}首先把這張被單蓋滿桌面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 真琴 用這支筆畫個五芒星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}五芒星…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 不用尺就能畫這麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔女從小就得學畫工整的五芒星了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}待會也教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}畫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就像這樣 在五芒星頂點放上蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏看看就好 畢竟有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼基礎魔法陣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後確認一下方位角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}把買來的點心放在北邊和南邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再將手遮在魔法陣上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}詠唱「賜予這些點心以祝福與強大力量吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}每個步驟都好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}賜予這些點心以祝福與強大力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}放著別管 等蠟燭熄滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒想到魔法原來這麼樸素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}華麗的魔法會比較困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}等她們更熟練點再教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看來蠟燭要燒一段時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 不知道滅了會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說不定會出現什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我知道了 零食就是祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}蠟燭快點熄滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要是蠟燭中途熄滅 魔法就失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}失敗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是的 謂之「滅之一根‧功虧一簣之卷」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不要滅 不要滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不憋氣也不會滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 魔法陣要從外側的圓畫起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還是不太像圓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}集中精神 一口氣畫完不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再試一次 這樣這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐 蠟燭全部熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔 那就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 這下吃了點心的人會中個小魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我來吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}學習新魔法時 最好就是親身體驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐也會靠體驗學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒事的 不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}加油 真琴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像什麼都沒有發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}OKOK 你試著看一下圭正在看的電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔法超成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼回事 感覺好傷心好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}吃了這個就會變成愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是看見什麼都會號啕大哭的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抱歉抱歉 效果也就一小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晚餐吃燉牛肉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這只是個小魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我最喜歡燉牛肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了 看你高興得直掉眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就做這道菜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我能不能嚐嚐這種？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏挑戰者 勇敢地嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}他開了好多槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}吃這種反而會特別愛笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏千夏 快看看真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像稍微緩和了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}奇多的鼻子光溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯尼小姐的也很光滑呀
